Data modeling for a social media app.

    Features

users can sign into the app with their email and password

users can follow each other

users can create posts with photos and/or text

users can comment on posts

users can join groups

users can create posts within groups


    Brainstorming

userName email password age
groupName posts comments
photos following groupMembers


    TABLE IDEAS 
Users       stores user information, for sign in ect.
posts       contains the info about a post, who created it and the text content of post
photos      contains photos and the post they relate to
comments    contain the user who left the comment, the post it was left on, and the body of the comment
groups      contains the name of the group summary
members     userId groupId
groupPosts  postId groupId



relationships

one => many
many => many
one => one
